      "createdAt": "2023-05-16T01:11:31.498Z",
      "author": "bade (Mikada)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello, <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> community!</p>\n<p>We are thrilled to announce the launch of our latest app  <a href=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=7a3bc27cbafba3161872c4bcf1c2f309&amp;response_type=install\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Private Notes and Comments</a> which allows you to start a private conversation with your collogues under the item view.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=7a3bc27cbafba3161872c4bcf1c2f309&amp;response_type=install\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Private Notes and Comments</a> also allow you to keep your private personal notes under the notes item view.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/9/8/98b756e795cda8d3a3395d18d6b7270ccbec31aa.png\" alt=\"app_card\" width=\"592\" height=\"348\" /><br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/d/3de509ee5c8386cd84a7489aad96f6ca423df29f.png\" title=\"pnc_image_1\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/d/3de509ee5c8386cd84a7489aad96f6ca423df29f_2_690x345.png\" alt=\"pnc_image_1\" width=\"690\" height=\"345\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">pnc_image_1</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 204 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/7/4727cd6133e2b5c40746aeee9806ca5b5403c4f0.png\" title=\"pnc_image_2\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/7/4727cd6133e2b5c40746aeee9806ca5b5403c4f0_2_690x345.png\" alt=\"pnc_image_2\" width=\"690\" height=\"345\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">pnc_image_2</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 149 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/a/0af2576c836b9fb1584087ecf47e913bb3d28408.png\" title=\"pnc_image_3\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/a/0af2576c836b9fb1584087ecf47e913bb3d28408_2_690x345.png\" alt=\"pnc_image_3\" width=\"690\" height=\"345\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">pnc_image_3</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 147 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 176108,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2024-04-01T12:03:46.849Z",
      "author": "bade (Mikada)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>\"\"<a href=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=7a3bc27cbafba3161872c4bcf1c2f309&amp;response_type=install\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Private Notes and Comments 4.4.0</a> Now avaliable with <strong>New features,</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Search comments</li>\n<li>Reply comments</li>\n<li>Mention by clicking the mention button</li>\n<li>Edit comments</li>\n<li>Insert link to the comments</li>\n<li>Change text color</li>\n<li>Highlight text</li>\n<li>Insert Code with desired programming language</li>\n<li>Insert Table</li>\n<li>Add emojis to the comments</li>\n<li>Like comments</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please add new item views called Private Comments+,Board Owner Only Private Comments+,Private Notes+ item views to your boards to use app.<br />\nOld item views of the app will be depricated in 30/05/2025.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/b/2bb63ba6d14d373c80c74a0219b98e3a3f25058b.png\" alt=\"Write private comments from guest members and viewers of the board Kopyası Kopyası (1)\" width=\"592\" height=\"348\" /></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/4/d461fb21735dea49e9b320b4254b22d5eee9a225.jpeg\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-04-01 at 18.01.40\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/d/4/d461fb21735dea49e9b320b4254b22d5eee9a225_2_690x338.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-04-01 at 18.01.40\" width=\"690\" height=\"338\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-04-01 at 18.01.40</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×942 95.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/6/3634ff3852e44ee2b48ccb4ab46440be4b7fd521.jpeg\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-04-01 at 17.59.40\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/6/3634ff3852e44ee2b48ccb4ab46440be4b7fd521_2_583x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-04-01 at 17.59.40\" width=\"583\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-04-01 at 17.59.40</span><span class=\"informations\">1078×924 96.6 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
